column5: Its finally here....24 hours or so from now will be heading north for two weeks....(including travel). Takes forever to get here but ends so quick. Will report upon return.
Enjoy!Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk
The journey can be p/o the fun part/gratification. This includes the planning and anticipation, as well as the actual drive/flight. Enjoy it all, best time of the year to be in the north woods! Bill
Could not agree more with time of year. Chilly mornings, fire in cabin, food, friends, and beer!! Oh, and maybe a fish or two!
From one Buckeye to another, where are you headed north of the border ? Safe travels....both on the roadways and on the water. Rich B
